Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:48.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,晩冬の山に 小さく低く 囁くような音が聞こえると
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:57.30,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そろそろか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:06.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じき一斉に 春の蟲が目を覚ます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:19.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それは山々のヌシ達が目覚めの日取りを相談する声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:00.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,参ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,啓蟄までにゃ この光脈筋抜けたかったが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,思いの外 今年は早そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:15.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,啓蟄後の蟲どもは 腹減らしてて厄介だしな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,呼ばれているが仕方無い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう急ぐ用でもねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,数日隠るか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:05.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだまだ寒いなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが 目が覚めりゃもう春だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.35,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もういい頃かね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.99,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妙に静かだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:53.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだこりゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:06.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,くそっ 読みを外したか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうなってんだ こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.34,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,とっくに雪融けしていい頃だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,颪笛までまだ嫌がる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:27.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さすがに もう真冬の勢いはないようだが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,向こうの山は雪がもうない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.81,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,日当たりのせいか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:54.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,颪笛の渡りだ 北へ帰ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この山の群れは まだ合流しないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:30.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,戻っちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと下ってんのに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何で来た道に戻ろんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山が…閉じている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山に入った時はなんともなかったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,参ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:16.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,冬の蟲が 渡りができずにいるのもそのせいか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体 何があったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌシに会ってみるか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,声が…しない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:47.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ムグラの気配も消えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒で呼び出すか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:57.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや 何があるか分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,止めておこう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここのヌシは…と
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,沢を辿ればいるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,地道に探すか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌシどころか 獣一匹いねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかしよく見れば あちこちに山崩れの跡があるな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:13.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,恐らく秋頃 台風に遭った跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,かなりの規模だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その傷を癒すため
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:24.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌシは山を閉じて 山ごと冬眠させているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:30.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが 弱った生物にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:33.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,冬眠はそのまま死んでしまうこともある賭け
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,隣の山じゃもう春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:44.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なのに まだ息を吹き返さないということは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.59,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう この山は死を待つのみ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ俺も巻き添えか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今 何かに見られてた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,水が…凍っていない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌシだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい ヌシ殿よ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつまで山を閉じたままなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もうあきらめてくれねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.39,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,外はもうとうに春なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.99,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ 集まってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:27.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっちへ来る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ この沼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:45.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,底なしか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,泥の中のようだが 呼吸ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆 眠っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:00.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒が湧き出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆 ここで体を癒していたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:21.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだ山は死んじゃいなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:37.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,春…なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:15.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだ颪笛がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒を…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:21.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい よせ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,渡ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山が 開いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やばい 始まった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,くそっ これじゃ蟲煙草も全滅だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さて 急ぐか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:56.71,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,抜けた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,思ったより楽に出られたな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山が本調子でないせいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:26.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それとも ヌシが蟲どもを抑えてくれてたか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:32.23,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかし 光酒まで失くしたのは痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:37.59,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ 弱った颪笛が渡りをするには必要な養分なんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まさか 俺を山に入れたのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒目当てでか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:41.39,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,全部 ヌシ殿の掌の上か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:52.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ いいか 世は春だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:22:03.39,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,冬は往き 山は笑い 野は錦
